synopsis.text: Alfeim Online beckons Kirito and his friends with an underwater quest to witness the majesty of a whale, a wish Yui holds dear. Meanwhile, in the real world, a summer day unfolds as Asuna, Lisbeth, and Silica take on a mission of their own: to help Leafa conquer her fear of water and teach her to swim. As the girls embark on their aquatic adventure, Kirito finds himself in an emergency meeting, reminiscing about their past exploits and uncovering hidden truths. With Kirito's reunion with a mysterious figure on the horizon, will Leafa overcome her fears in time to join the underwater quest, or will the depths of Alfeim Online hold more surprises for our heroes? Join Kirito and his friends as they navigate challenges in both the virtual and real worlds, forging unbreakable bonds along the way.
